WEBVTT

00:02:27.345 --> 00:02:31.008
Kwa miaka miwili, pasipo kuepukika, 
ajenda za habari zilisonga mbele,

00:02:31.032 --> 00:02:32.762
na kwa miaka miwili,

00:02:32.786 --> 00:02:35.945
hatukusikia sana 
kuhusu wasichana wa Chibok.

00:02:35.969 --> 00:02:37.838
Kila moja alidhania wamekwishakufa.

00:02:38.233 --> 00:02:40.220
Lakini Aprili mwaka jana,

00:02:40.244 --> 00:02:42.449
niliweza kupata video hii.

00:02:43.036 --> 00:02:44.776
Hii ni picha-mnato toka kwenye video

00:02:44.800 --> 00:02:47.914
ambayo Boko Haram walirekodi 
kama ushahidi kuwa wako hai,

00:02:48.923 --> 00:02:51.467
na kupitia chanzo kimoja, 
nilipata video hii.

00:02:52.109 --> 00:02:53.646
Lakini kabla sijaichapisha,

00:02:53.670 --> 00:02:56.695
Nilihitaji kusafiri 
kwenda kaskazini mashariki mwa Naijeria

00:02:56.719 --> 00:02:58.786
kuzungumza na wazazi, kuihakikisha.

00:02:59.317 --> 00:03:02.694
Sikuhitaji kusubiri sana 
kupata uthibitisho.